data.description: Nestled in the heart of Humble, this stunning 4-bed, 3-bath gem boasts 3,268 sq ft of pure elegance. The open-concept living space is bathed in natural light, with high ceilings and exquisite hardwood floors. The gourmet kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a spacious island for culinary adventures. Relax in the master suite, complete with a spa-like en-suite bath and a walk-in closet. The backyard oasis awaits with a covered patio/ pool/ Cabana Pool Room and lush landscaping, perfect for entertaining. Conveniently located near top-rated schools, shopping, and dining, this home offers the perfect blend of luxury and functionality. Don't miss the chance to make 19118 Keyturn Ln your forever home!
